    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Try 2 Sleep》是一款为单次游玩而设计的短时高强度合作恐怖体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你的搭档刚刚搬进一栋新房，却很快意识到这里隐藏着某种无法解释的邪恶力量。在这场混乱而危险的夜晚，你们的噩梦逐渐成真，而真正的安眠将变得不可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238310/extras/437fb0f508d07ddb0dc8f9108fd9902b.poster.avif?t=1771162701\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238310/extras/437fb0f508d07ddb0dc8f9108fd9902b.webm?t=1771162701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238310/extras/437fb0f508d07ddb0dc8f9108fd9902b.mp4?t=1771162701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们是否足够默契？只有不断沟通、精准配合，才能在这座被诅咒的房屋中存活下来。任何一次失误，都可能导致失败。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238310/extras/90ebc419c17a5f2b4b6e0d4e4605a867.poster.avif?t=1771162701\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238310/extras/90ebc419c17a5f2b4b6e0d4e4605a867.webm?t=1771162701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238310/extras/90ebc419c17a5f2b4b6e0d4e4605a867.mp4?t=1771162701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >睡眠可以恢复体力，但同时也会推动夜晚向前，使房屋变得更加危险。你们必须在风险与生存之间做出选择，寻找逃离房屋的钥匙，并揭开花园大门之外隐藏的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238310/extras/c53583368bffa241e8e5b32b340faabc.poster.avif?t=1771162701\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238310/extras/c53583368bffa241e8e5b32b340faabc.webm?t=1771162701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238310/extras/c53583368bffa241e8e5b32b340faabc.mp4?t=1771162701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持两人本地合作游玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可通过 Steam 远程同乐与好友在线合作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持单人游玩，但生存难度将大幅提升。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由邪恶的人工智能控制房屋，每一夜都会带来不同的恐怖体验。</p></li></ul>",
